PrecisAmendments to the WILDLIFE AREA REGULATIONS which provide for the establishment of two new National Wildlife Areas, namely PORTOBELLO CREEK in New Brunswick and NIRJUTIQAVVIK in the Northwest Territories, and for the expansion of four existing ones, namely Cap Tourmente, Lac Saint- François, Pointe-au-Père and Pointe de l'Est, all in Quebec.
